com.cyc.session

Interface SessionOptions.DefaultSessionOptions

  • Enclosing interface:
    SessionOptions

    public static interface SessionOptions.DefaultSessionOptions
    An immutable set of options, including the name of the cyclist making assertions, and the project's KE purpose. This provides the defaults for the mutable SessionOptions interface.
